cave-wasm-runtime
=================

This crate is a clean-room *concept port* — it does not vendor or copy source
from the projects below; it reimplements documented behaviour in safe Rust.
It is published under the Apache License 2.0 (see the `license` field in
Cargo.toml), NOT the cave-runtime workspace-default AGPL-3.0.

Behaviour and ABI shapes are referenced from:

  bytecodealliance/wasmtime   — Apache-2.0 WITH LLVM-exception
      https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime
      (binary decoder, execution semantics, fuel metering, WASI preview1 ABI)

  wasmerio/wasmer             — MIT
      https://github.com/wasmerio/wasmer
      (runtime / registry shapes)

  spinframework/spin          — Apache-2.0
      https://github.com/spinframework/spin
      (content-addressed module registry, serverless trigger model)

SHA-256 follows FIPS 180-4. No third-party code is bundled.
